<subSubSection pageId="67" pageNumber="1026" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="67.[151,1058,617,668]" pageId="67" pageNumber="1026">
E t y m o l o g y: The trivial name, 
<emphasis box="[548,596,617,638]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="1026">taxis</emphasis>
, is a Greek name with a meaning of &quot;line&quot;; with reference to the lines on the elytral disc.
</paragraph>
